h means the classifier's\nperformance on previous tasks is enhanced rather than compromised while\nlearning a new task.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 26 Mar 2022 09:28:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Jun 2022 03:18:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
